title: [Western Waterway, Harbor]
description: Lanterns dangle from several small fishing boats occupying this area, their nets floating languidly in the water and glistening with moonlight as it reflects from the attached floats.  Occasionally, a crew member will appear and check on a net, but most of the boats are quiet as the fisherman sleep.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
